org.openscience.cdk

Class AtomParity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.AtomParity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, IAtomParity, ICDKObject, IStereoElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DebugAtomParity, NNAtomParity

    public class AtomParity
extends Object
implements IAtomParity, Serializable
    Represents the concept of an atom parity identifying the stereochemistry around an atom, given four neighbouring atoms.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
    Keywords:
    atom parity, stereochemistry
